  "title": "Digital Marketing Executive",
  "description": "<p>Plan, execute and manage all digital marketing channels with innovative ideas (e.g., company websites, social media, etc.) to ensure brand consistency.</p><ul><li>Regularly generate, edit, publish and update company websites, social media posts, stories, and other sharable content</li><li>Creating and copywriting advertising assets in the form of copy, video and images</li><li>Manage and improve online content and track SEO efforts.</li><li>Brainstorm new and creative growth strategies through digital marketing and be open to experimenting with new channels.</li><li>Any ad hoc tasks as assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirement:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Preferably at least 3 years of relevant working experience</li><li>Familiar with Microsoft Office and Excel</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please email to mingfa.matters@gmail.com</p>",
